msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid "To view the connections, issue the following command:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"~]$&nbsp;<command>nmcli con show conf</command>\n"
"NAME        UUID                                 TYPE           TIMESTAMP-"
"REAL\n"
"eth0        4d5c449a-a6c5-451c-8206-3c9a4ec88bca 802-3-ethernet Mon 21 Oct "
"2013 16:01:53 BST\n"
"bridge-br0  79cf6a3e-0310-4a78-b759-bda1cc3eef8d bridge         never"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<firstterm>Spanning tree protocol</firstterm> (<acronym>STP</acronym>) "
"according to the IEEE 802.1D standard is enabled by default. To disable "
"<systemitem class=\"protocol\">STP</systemitem> for this bridge, issue a "
"command as follows:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#, no-c-format
msgid "~]$&nbsp;<command>nmcli con bridge-br0 stp no</command>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To re-enable <systemitem class=\"protocol\">802.1D STP</systemitem> for this "
"bridge, issue a command as follows:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#, no-c-format
msgid "~]$&nbsp;<command>nmcli con bridge-br0 stp yes</command>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default bridge priority for <systemitem class=\"protocol\">802.1D STP</"
"systemitem> is <literal>32768</literal>. The lower number is preferred in "
"root bridge selection. For example, a bridge with priority of "
"<literal>28672</literal> would be selected as the root bridge in preference "
"to a bridge with priority value of <literal>32768</literal> (the default). "
"To create a bridge with a non-default value, issue a command as follows:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"~]$&nbsp;<command>nmcli con add type bridge ifname br5 stp yes priority "
"28672</command>\n"
"Connection 'bridge-br5' (86b83ad3-b466-4795-aeb6-4a66eb1856c7) successfully "
"added."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The allowed values are in the range <literal>0</literal> to <literal>65535</"
"literal>, but can only be set in multiples of <literal>4096</literal>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the bridge priority of an existing bridge to a non-default value, "
"issue a command in the following format:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"~]$&nbsp;<command>nmcli connection modify bridge-br5 bridge.priority 36864</"
"command>"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Further options for <systemitem class=\"protocol\">802.1D STP</systemitem> "
"are listed in the bridge section of the <filename>nmcli(1)</filename> man "
"page."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
